  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/16/google-maps-update-for-ios-brings-in-line-route-previews/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/google-maps-ios-route-previews.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nGoogle 今天对 iOS 版的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/16/google-maps-2-for-ios/\">Google Maps</a> 进行了升级，新版中加入了导航预览，让用户可以结合实时交通信息对 Google 提供的路线进行选择，这样就可以避免拥挤的路段了。除此之外 Google 还特意为初用者准备了新手指南，而且新版本也开始支持阿拉伯语和希伯来语了。目前更新已在 App Store 中上线，相关链接可在引用来源中找到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/15/google-maps-update-for-ios-brings-in-line-route-previews/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/10/15/google-maps-for-ios-update-speeds-access-to-navigation-adds-new-languages\" target=\"_blank\">AppleInsider</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/google-maps/id585027354\" target=\"_blank\">App Store</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/16/google-maps-update-for-ios-brings-in-line-route-previews/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20746660/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/16/google-maps-update-for-ios-brings-in-line-route-previews/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
